title: Thursday Post Show (11-03-22)
itunes:title: Thursday Post Show (11-03-22)
description:
Bobby talks about having to get ready for the CMAs next week. Lunchbox gets some not so great news about his seats. You get a peek behind the scenes with what Bobby does after the show. A woman who is renting out her husband, a man who was secretly living on campus, and a kid’s hospital that turned down money linked to gambling.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
